        {
            "title": "分析人士稱若韓元跌向心理關口1,500 韓國可能會加大捍衛本幣力度",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"分析人士稱若韓元跌向心理關口1,500 韓國可能會加大捍衛本幣力度\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/m__1YdT0dUFQRta3b9Fo.A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-11/afea32b0-b225-11ef-bbef-22313f548ab8\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">分析人士稱若韓元跌向心理關口1,500 韓國可能會加大捍衛本幣力度</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB%E7%A8%B1%E8%8B%A5%E9%9F%93%E5%85%83%E8%B7%8C%E5%90%91%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E9%97%9C%E5%8F%A31-500-%E9%9F%93%E5%9C%8B%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%9C%83%E5%8A%A0%E5%A4%A7%E6%8D%8D%E8%A1%9B%E6%9C%AC%E5%B9%A3%E5%8A%9B%E5%BA%A6-022701959.html",
